      "category": "biomes",
      "entity_domain": "environment",
      "entity_subtype": "biome",
      "excerpt": "A scorched basalt plateau with fissure vents and sparse heat-tolerant flora stretching between cooled lava rivers.",
      "body_html_sanitized": "<p><strong>Cinder Basalt Flats</strong> stretch between cooled lava rivers and active vent clusters across the eastern volcanic belt.</p><p>Wind carries fine ash that settles in ripple patterns across dark stone fields. Explorers note reduced visibility during thermal updrafts.</p>",
